We analyzed the quality of the DoCo dataset by comparing automatic relation extractions to extractions given by human annotators.
A sample of {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0058||FO}} documents was selected, {{arxiv_2111_13611_FO0059||FO}} per relation, with half from the high-coverage range and the rest from the low-coverage range. Each document was annotated with all correct tuples for the document's main subject entity.